text:
Located in open air food centre at Kovan.

Long queue at dinner time as it's a favorite dessert. Must be good based on Singaporeans eating habits.

3 chef hawker stall.

$3 for a bowl of 4 ballings.
The cooking staff is rude when asked about the price of the soup base only, and the balling is very thick and sticky (not nice) very different from other stalls I ate.
I recommend this uncle to use skillsfuture to take hospitality courses..
